/purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1331:"<p><a href="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/matt.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-8607" src="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/matt-198x300.jpg" alt="matt" width="198" height="300" /></a>WDS is proud to announce our newest team member, <a title="Matt McAchran" href="http://webdevstudios.com/team/matt-mcachran/">Matt McAchran</a>! He is joining us as a developer.</p>\n<p>Matt is a developer from Virginia Beach who has been in the IT field for over a dozen years. He started doing computer networking in High School and was introduced to web development shortly after. After a brief hiatus from development to attend school for accounting, he decided that web development was a lot more fun. He was introduced to WordPress in 2009 and after working with several other content management systems he’s come to the conclusion that WordPress is simply the best.</p>\n<p>Matt is awaiting the birth of his son and enjoys spending time with his wife and two dogs. In his free time, he loves to play disc golf and spend time relaxing on the beach. You can follow <a href="https://twitter.com/mmcachran">Matt on Twitter</a> to keep up with baby news!</p>\n<p>We are thrilled to have Matt joining our team and can&#8217;t wait to see what he will bring to our already amazing team!</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://webdevstudios.com/2014/10/15/wds-welcomes-matt-mcachran/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";